channel.name: CBBC UK
channel.title: Dennis & Gnasher Unleashed!
channel.desc: The gang spot what appears to be a meteor through Screwtop's mega-powerful telescope. It turns out to be an early space invention of the Professor's, hurtling back towards Earth on a collision course with Beanotown! Can Dennis and the gang save the day, or will Beanotown be destroyed for ever.
